Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【開場語】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我的鼻子沒有聞錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈到底裝在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在這種情況下 還能裝出一副無辜的樣子真是好膽量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是否要讓我來問問你的身體呢

Comment: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:50.97,chop,,0000,0000,0000,,【OP：瞳の中の迷宫】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.14,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:42.39,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思念越發強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.52,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無法傳達到這份祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:53.11,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}一定是因為	迷失了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:01:00.83,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無論何時  只有被映在這眼瞳裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.29,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.46,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}一直如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.63,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}世界並非唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:15.38,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}還有所謂如果的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.39,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}因為存在著無限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:25.02,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}正迷失著方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.77,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.77,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}不論你現在身處何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:33.98,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}必定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:39.66,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}不慎闖入了瞳中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.33,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:45.58,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被黑暗之手遮蔽了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.71,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被怯弱的心所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.50,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:56.09,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}繼續尋找著

Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.14,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:42.39,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思いつのるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.52,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}この祈りが届かないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:53.11,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}何かをきっと 見失ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:01:00.83,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いつだって この瞳に 映されたものだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.29,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}唯一の真実だと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.46,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}信じていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.63,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}世界は一つじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:15.38,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}もしもという世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.39,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無限にあるとして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:25.02,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いま途方に暮れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.77,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.77,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いま何処にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:33.98,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}必ず見つけ出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:39.66,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷い込んだのは瞳の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.33,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:45.58,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}例え暗闇がゆく手を遮り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.71,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}弱気な心惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.50,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}諦めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:56.09,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}探しつづけるから

Comment: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(800,1000)\be1\bord2\4a&Hc1&\3a&Hc1&\shad3\pos(523,365)}蓉 子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快點坦白 可是會讓這個身體受傷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼非得待在這麼寒冷的地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種黑暗而又狹窄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:03:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是既寬闊風景又好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片漆黑 什麼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊賞著雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很風雅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看周圍 冰天雪地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一片漆黑什麼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事能稱得上什麼風雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙熱的酒一下子就結成冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在在在幹什麼呀 這可不是開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣去會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手呀 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼 惡魔 神不會饒恕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小健結成冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊 兄弟 要不要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一副慌張的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒有 沒有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 這個那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是慌慌張張\N急急忙忙的 到底是爲了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人太少 完全賣不出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正最初就沒什麼期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你知道初美在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒説謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 有一套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,説是去找房間裏的男子 就再也沒看見他的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可疑了 快去找出那個男子來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找房間裏的男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是前面那閒客房的旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴突然感到腹痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我正在到處詢問有誰帶了藥來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那真是不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 只能一個個挨著搜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題好像不是你同伴的腹痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有帶就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出去的話 可是又會遭遇同樣的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是肌肉 那個胸脯的鼓起也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰看到都會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我到也聼過有那種興趣的女性\N在男裝時會想辦法將胸脯隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天老是踫到同行的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人想讓你見一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連禮服都借用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是生意上的東西 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你非常適合這身打扮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西伯利亞之虎 這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爲什麼要來直接與我接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我告訴她這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是根據實際情況的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在知道相互的身份才能處於有利的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被手冊或是命令束縛住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一行中可是很難生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面沒人嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來陪陪我吧 喂 裡面有人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您這樣我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回你的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煩我 別以爲我是二等乘客就小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 請回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在進行一個重要的商談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否請不要打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,説是商談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 你這樣讓我很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣的商談啊 能否也讓我參加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否把暗號解讀本交給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否請您安靜一點呢 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不是一般的乘務員與醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 果然先裝上保險是正確的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保險?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛列車被裝上了炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定能時間内 我不去復位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和列車一起 解讀本也會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死了那麼就一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 別小看人 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來可是這位姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解讀本 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在哪裡 到底放在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想在這個亞爾卡迪亞 做出藍色的天空的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺到不在這個空中庭園 做出一個向日葵的小山是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 説到對於向日葵的小山來説 必要的東西 還是教會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼説來 你們還想參加我的造城活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那真是奇妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得有人確實說過下次在我面前出現時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對、一定會將那個 智慧之光的根源夏娃一起帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不是 哪裡弄錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有說過\N“絕對”、“一定”之類的話的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能得到夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家就會比現在更加的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如是這樣的話 爲什麼夏娃不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格爾剛裘亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過生氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓皮膚開裂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你擔心非常的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:14:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就讓塞倫來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你們所知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一個純粹的妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是屬於惡魔的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她將出手幫助我們尋找夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接著就讓我們\N回到夜行列車的故事裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底變成什麼樣子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼…會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒被打中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在問出之前就把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 多少也知道了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個乘務員與這個男人是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是西伯利來之虎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是 也有需要扮演那個角色的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 時代已經變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種三流的男人竟然被派到第一線來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當當你的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是很適合那身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這項工作來説 最需要到不是體力或年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是經驗啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號本一定就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剛才從那年輕男人那裡得到的東西交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不反抗就不會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底藏在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從那男人那裡拿到了什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這東西給你的男人\N在這輛列車是裝了定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有什麼線索
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人從一等車廂的洗手間出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人從這裡出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在拍掉什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經找到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空的 裡面什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麼 爲什麼會沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是葉月的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你到底去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打開了打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到一個時鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣真好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是保護我自己而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲你是一個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業罷了 一點也高興不起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界已沒有什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個旅行到底會持續到何時呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點找到夏娃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的身體先撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光看著出神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著走啊 喂！

Comment: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:33.84,jped,,0000,0000,0000,,【ED：永遠の祈りを捧げて】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:41.65,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠の祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:48.37,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.29,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}どんなに遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.67,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}きっと捕まえてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:10.43,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕との それが約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:17.48,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思いでも 抱きしめないでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:24.90,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}気持ちは 一つも届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:33.29,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠お祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.04,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:48.93,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕の間にひかる夜明けをみつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:58.06,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,500)}もらすぐ始まる明日を迎えにゆく

Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:41.65,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}獻上永遠的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:48.37,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}切莫放棄珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.29,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無論多麼遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.67,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}也一定要抓住給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:10.43,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}那是你我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:17.48,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使抱著回憶哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:24.90,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}任何心情也無法傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:33.29,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}獻上永遠的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.04,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}切莫放棄珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:48.93,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}去發現在你我之間閃亮的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:58.06,ched,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,500)}迎接即將開始的明天

Comment: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【下集預告】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這本夜行列車的書裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到初美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 還是偷看一下下一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「暗與帽子與書之旅人」
